reviewText: A fun, independent movie.  Worth taking a look at.

ive seen this about 3 times now...the first 30 minutes could be a great movie on its own, it was surprising and unpredictably thrilling...the middle was simply ok drama filler...the end is fairly good action chase to round it out

This is a exciting, film that keeps you on the edge of your seat the whole time. It is nice to see women who take charge for a change and be able to show their power. Get this movie you will not be disappointed as it is a well made film...

I seen this at its premier and the movie is fantastic. The filmmakers worked hard on this project and it shows. If you like independent films, I would suggest you buy this one. Not like other indie projects that have big budgets and big actors, this one is truly independent from Hollywood and just as good as things you'd see in the theaters.
